strings:
<voice_0x01001916><se_low>Kalderasha: .........
So, now we know how it happened.
What a terrible end for poor Rylus.
<voice_0x01001917><se_low>King Trode: Had I only known what a fiend that jester was, I would never have let him cross the threshold!
<voice_0x01001919><se_low>King Trode: But Rylus was a careless master, I must say.
<voice_0x0100191A><se_low>King Trode: One must be in touch with one's servants' needs and moods. It's little wonder he met such a ‘sticky’ end. Ha ha ha! ...Ahem!
<voice_0x0100191B><se_low>Kalderasha: There is nothing more to see in my crystal ball today. Go.
<voice_0x0100191C><se_low>Kalderasha: When next you come, the Great Kalderasha will tell for you another fortune...though maybe not for free.
